                <h1>Applying Wallpaper to Textured Walls: What You Need to Know</h1>
                <p>Yes, wallpaper can be applied to textured walls, but special considerations are needed. Use thicker wallpaper or vinyl types that can better adhere to uneven surfaces. It's essential to clean and possibly prime the wall for a smoother application. Always follow the manufacturer's recommendations for optimal results.</p>
